1. User Management (Optional for simple version)
Register/Login
Track individual portfolios

2. Stock Listings
List of available stocks (name, symbol, price)
Simulated or real-time prices (API or mock data)

3. Trading Operations
Buy Stock: Enter stock symbol, quantity, buy at current price.
Sell Stock: Sell previously bought stock from user portfolio.
Balance checking and transaction validation.

4. Portfolio Tracking
Show holdings: stock name, quantity, average buy price, current value.
Profit/loss calculation.

5. Transaction History
Log of buy/sell operations with timestamps and prices.
